{"tid":694862,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"行出街，最討厭一定係中佬","createTime":"2018-06-08T16:50:21.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-09T13:33:11.000Z","uid":127972,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"adc52701a1358a7a8cd1bb9db1a7c6e1b4fb61c7","tid":694862,"uid":127972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T16:50:21.000Z","msg":"咁多種社會族群，最討厭一定係中佬，<br />\n專蝦蝦霸霸，行路想撞人就撞人，入地鐵人多照撞入來，從不禮讓，見解自以為是。<br />\n<br />\n上次坐巴士停站，下層企位人多，上層有個中佬以為自己係Hulk 咁行落來撞開人<br />\n<br />\n又有一次，繁忙時段坐巴士，中佬放背囊，明知冇乜位，望到人都不為所動。<br />\n<br />\n中佬欺善怕惡，女人始終係死穴<br />\n睇完呢條片，雖然港女也並非善男順女，但總算是大快人心。<br />\n<a href=\"https://streamable.com/1ahd4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstreamable.com%2F1ahd4&d=seGefaui7ep6fXMu%2BzFu4TA5unq%2FSd9ZKvr75NUD1%2F0%3D&h=c33873fb\" target=\"_blank\">https://streamable.com/1ahd4</a><br />\n<br />\n利申：上次行行下街被中佬撞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d58d3d9d3a740b6dfad574a1d19fd951923b8657","tid":694862,"uid":127972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T16:51:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a622ce163a7dc040fe756b497fb396f63884adf3","tid":694862,"uid":104225,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T16:54:58.000Z","msg":"香港大部分老一輩都係咗架啦<br />\n先落後上教咗十年都唔閪識<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n利申90"},{"pid":"db1eb8fad9d980cf36c3753b20c0a969a57a39f6","tid":694862,"uid":127972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:22:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f71370b32684bf5f8dedc6193fc52c859f9f78e3","tid":694862,"uid":30850,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-08T17:32:48.000Z","msg":"次次咳又大大聲，口水呀痰呀四圍吐，火車頭，咪都係呢班廢中"},{"pid":"f7eb92336c52fe85074919ff7a028ff87319477b","tid":694862,"uid":23116,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"